H0.text: What number on the Beaufort Scale describes the wind as gale. 5

H1.text: What number on the Beaufort Scale describes the wind as gale. 9

H2.text: What number on the Beaufort Scale describes the wind as gale. 6

H3.text: What number on the Beaufort Scale describes the wind as gale. 8

A4.text: Gale Warnings are issued if winds of Beaufort force 8 are expected.

A5.text: Strong Gale Warnings are issued if winds of Beaufort force 9 or frequent gusts of at least 52 knots are expected.
